{"title":"丰收谣","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":10,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收歌声冲云霄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗遍地处处飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收歌声冲云霄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满坝谷子黄橙橙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年增产万万挑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷子收来千万担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷子收来堆成山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算账派们抬头看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“啊哟！太多算不完。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今人智慧大无边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亩田收入几万斤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些奇迹数不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强过古人万万千。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今朝奇迹数不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如天上满天星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古人比今差得远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如巴掌比青天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（贵州荔波县莫廷坤）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄金山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前山靠后山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左右山连山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉米山，稻儿山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山高直上白云间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×　　×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷儿山，大豆山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼前一片黄金山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄金山，五谷山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民歌唱丰收年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（沈阳市赵再庸）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}